  "Title": "An update for vim is now available for openEuler-24.03-LTS-SP4,openEuler-20.03-LTS-SP4,openEuler-22.03-LTS-SP4,openEuler-24.03-LTS-SP1,openEuler-24.03-LTS-SP3",
